README
------

librem - "Audio and video processing media library"
Copyright (C) 2010 - 2011 Creytiv.com

Distributed under BSD license




Audio Modules:

  name:     status:       description:

* aubuf     -             Audio buffer
* aufile    -             Audio file player/recorder (WAV etc.)
* aumix     -             Audio mixer
* auresamp  -             Audio resampler
* autone    -             Tone/DTMF generator
* g711      -             G.711 audio codec
* g722      -             G.722 audio codec



Video Modules:

  name:     status:       description:

* vidbase   -             Base video types
* vidconv   -             Colorspace conversion (incl. rotation)
* viddraw   -             Basic drawing routines
* vidfilt   -             Video filters (alphablending, blurring, ...)
* vidmix    -             Video mixer



External dependencies:

- FFmpeg libswscale (for colorspace conversion)
